FBIS4-35981 "drnes108_n_94015" FBIS-NES-94-108 Daily Report 6 Jun 1994 LEBANON Further Reinforcements Reported Further Reinforcements Reported NC0606053194 Beirut Radio Lebanon in Arabic 0430 GMT 6 Jun 94 NC0606053194 Beirut Radio Lebanon Arabic BFN [Text] According to reports from the south this morning, a state of caution continues to prevail in the liberated areas adjacent to the occupied border strip. This strip, meanwhile, has been the scene of Israeli military activities and reinforcements.
